## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all survival stories or strategies from Auschwitz. Survivor accounts can vary significantly, and the experiences documented here represent only a fraction of the diverse survival narratives. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources means that some details may be subject to interpretation or bias.